channel.title: My RuneScape Pure
channel.description:
Well i havnt really played rs since i got my main banned (Dh713) and my pure banned (attackplease) for bug abuse.... anyways my friend made a pure after he got banned for helping me bug abuse. and his name was "Next Update" well recently he quit because of school that just started. So he gave me about 9m (7.5m in cash and 1.5m in runes) and a pretty damn good pure.
Also Rate My Pure - tell me if it is good for its lvl etc or if it is bad for its lvl
[b]Jagex Fucking banned me for no damn reason wtf!??!??! I have 10 out of 10 blackmarks[/b]
These are my Goals and what i plan to do:
-Get 82 mage -get 70 range -mage stake for money -alch to 94 mage -get 85+ range -start pking :)
[b]well i decided to take these screenys off and post one of my blackmarks instead... I am not ranting about this so its not agaisnt the rules i dont care that i got banned i can make another account its just that they banned me for no reason[/b]
